data.name: label5.Text
data.value:
Welcome to Arkham: Revived (Self-Hosted)!
This program will allow Batman: Arkham Origins to start and join matchmaking lobbies without using an external/third-party authentication or WBID server.
Before starting the server or launching the game, click "Setup" to force the game to use your local computer as its authentication server.
Afterwards, click "Start" and then launch the game as normal. It is recommended to set the launch option "-nostartupmovies" through Steam.
If you'd like to copy a lobby invite URL, set your Steam Web API Key and SteamID below.

data.name: label1.Text
data.value:
Customize attributes sent to Arkham Origins when connecting to the auth server.
Save Data contains your user configuration variables alongside other customization.
Message of the Day is displayed on top of the main menu.
Inventory manages what items appear in-game by UUID.
Catalog manages which items can be used in the inventory and stores by their UUIDs.
Item Store manages which items can be purchased in the store by UUID.
Credits Store manages the credits store for microtransactions by UUID.
